name: Mellon Collie and the Infinte Sadness
description: Homage to the third LP by the Smashing Pumpkins, that was released as a double album in 1995. I purchased it on CD shortly after it was released in the UK and put it on to tape so I could listen to it on my bus ride to school every morning. I had to omit a few tracks to make it fit the tape. The missing tracks, I discovered, where actually amongst my favourites from the whole LP, including Bodies.
